Install instructions:
1. Extract the .zip file
2. Drag the \&quot;the binding of isaac\&quot; folder to the applications folder
3. Start the game

\&quot;Binding_of_Isaac\&quot; starts the game with a loading screen
\&quot;Isaac\&quot; starts the game with no loading screen

Use with ever you want!	



